    "Id": "vehiclechassisdef_HI-SCOUT",
    "Name": "Hi-Scout",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Hi-Scout Drone Carrier</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>4/6 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>240 ICE</color></b>\n\nThe Hi-Scout Drone Carrier is a specialized reconnaissance vehicle. Designed to provide early warning and battlefield intelligence, its advanced tracking and communication systems made it a highly effective scout, particularly during the Succession Wars.\n\nArmed with only a single SRM-2 and one ton of ammunition, the Hi-Scout relies on stealth and evasion rather than direct combat. While 5.5 tons of ArcShield armor offer some protection against light scout vehicles, anything heavier would pose a significant threat.",
